Daily Log Keeper

Help:

1: Create a new log

	*Click the "plus" action button and simply fill out the fields with your desired information. Once you are satisfied hit the "diskette" to save your log, it will now appear in the list on the main page.

2: Edit an existing log

	*Click on the log you wish to edit and you will see the text fields populated with the data from your log. Simply make any corrections, additions, or deletions you want, then click the "diskette," once again, to save your log.

3: Send log(s) as an email

	*In the main view of the app, hold down on the log that you wish to email, you may select as many as you want, and you will be presented with an action menu. Clicking the share icon will prompt you to select which app you would like to use. Note: not all applications will support the full formating. Gmail and Google Drive are best suited for sharing your logs.

4: Deleting a log

	*In the main view, click the log you are wanting to delete, and any subsequent logs. You will be presented with an action menu, press the trash icon and you will be asked to confirm the deletion.